None of the Independent Non-Executive Directors have any pecuniary relationship or transactions with the Company, its promoters, its senior management or its subsidiary which in the judgement of Board may affect the independence of the director except receiving sitting fees for attending Board/Committee meetings and commission from the Company.

(B) Non-Executive Directors' compensation and disclosures

All fees and commission paid to Non-Executive Directors including independent directors are fixed by the Board of Directors. Consent of the Members of the Company is also obtained for commission paid to Non-Executive Directors including independent directors. The Company has no Employee Stock Option Scheme and hence, no stock options are granted to Non-Executive Directors, including independent directors.

